{"tid":1763442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[12.1港九一遊行] 有冇諗過點解黑警咁好死出哂不反對通知書？我哋逆地而處，睇下黑警點諗","createTime":"2019-11-30T10:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T16:20:43.000Z","uid":132625,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dfcea382867cbf0a394cc40dd9ce2b51f971223b","tid":1763442,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:43:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">[12.1] 有冇諗過點解黑警咁好死出哂不反對通知書？我哋逆地而處，睇下黑警點諗</span><br />\n<br />\n港九三個遊行全獲不反，代表咩呢？即係：<br />\n<br />\n(1) 警隊高層研判理大保衛戰之後，大部分勇武已經被捕或受重創，短期內唔敢再搞事<span style=\"color: gold;\">(機會50/50, 唔排除警隊高層有真心膠)</span>；<br />\n<br />\n(2) 警隊高層推算核心勇武人員仍然在逃，惟未能掌握潛在人數，借機引蛇出洞，不惜一切再一次大圍捕勇武<span style=\"color: gold;\">(most likely, consistent with HKPF&rsquo;s line of tactics)</span>；<br />\n<br />\n(3)政府高層害怕美國新生效的香港人權和民主法，為免招人話病，只好不反<span style=\"color: gold;\"> (possible but inconsistent with Carrie Lam&rsquo;s character, she may however listen to the counter-opinion in her cabinet)</span>；and/or<br />\n<br />\n(4) 區選大敗，民意清晰，不敢再刺激民憤<span style=\"color: gold;\"> (unlikely, since inconsistent with the character of Carrie or her cabinet)</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">結論：</span><br />\n<br />\n利申唔係休息撚，唔好屌我冷氣軍師住。聽日唔開戰唔係怕民意，民意一早企哂嚮我哋呢邊。唔開戰係因為策略。<br />\n<br />\n一來據知最近好缺乏文具，早前好多貨被海關扣起左，待美國Black Friday之後送貨到港又要等一段時間。由於中大理大保衛戰消耗了大量文具，未有新文具嘅手足無法上陣作戰。<br />\n<br />\n二來理大保衛戰有好多手足身心受創，要時間回血，戰力不足而打大戰，乃兵家大忌。<br />\n<br />\n三來可以返番去以下路線：和理非逼政府答應訴求，和理非設下死線，政府唔回應訴求，到時勇武又有用武之地。係，我知係左膠，有人話：「畫面靚咁又點？」但而家有唔少手足要休養，戰力不足嘅前題下，呢個星期咪當集中打和理非國際戰線囉。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為最快下星期可以正式變番十八區勇武 stand-by 模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1b77f526412234e235675a6f9eca7789655dfa","tid":1763442,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家抛磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f207fff7732d5a092ade9f9a1e8a8dd6e152e33","tid":1763442,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf80a84b25ee68892b5d720cc9e34bdc5f5e0d36","tid":1763442,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:48:42.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb2193532ea218ea0626bc32eb906f2d0ac469a","tid":1763442,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"08962e20d184bae700f3b0dc0bfc870d5aa4efd9","tid":1763442,"uid":137217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:56:46.000Z","msg":"文具真係無咗好多<br />\n可以真係幾次和理非集氣先"},{"pid":"23977b9040c7fa2fa3a93d6645bf3120d9a993bf","tid":1763442,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08962e20d184bae700f3b0dc0bfc870d5aa4efd9","tid":1763442,"uid":137217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:56:46.000Z","msg":"文具真係無咗好多<br />\n可以真係幾次和理非集氣先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T11:24:52.000Z","msg":"exact7ly"},{"pid":"3374982f2ee94aa68eec35a798c8a4ca917654dd","tid":1763442,"uid":29555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T11:42:33.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c0833d2cc7ebe2650cb87e793f2041bcfd8b5b","tid":1763442,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"集氣！"},{"pid":"7f89b326d5ab40540eb5b71d48ef099f75f2c019","tid":1763442,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T12:42:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f7a22c0129a88773fb84c8962caf72cb1557f53b","tid":1763442,"uid":178115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":